---
title: Grilled Tofu and Stone Fruit Salad with Basil Pesto
description: Enjoy all the flavours of summer in one amazing salad! Sweet nectarines shine with savoury basil pesto, and tomatoes and tender spinach balance together to compliment grilled tofu.
